cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.IR 

The paper deals with computer vision tasks such as object recognition, instance segmentation, and text recognition. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of generative models, which falls under the category of machine learning. Hence, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the second most likely category. The paper also involves natural language processing tasks such as text recognition, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning techniques, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper involves information retrieval tasks such as text recognition, which falls under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR).
